headline: This Magnificent Dividend Stock Is Looking to Tap Into an $18.8 Trillion Opportunity to Enhance Its Continued Growth
summary: Realty Income (NYSE: O) has done a magnificent job growing its portfolio, cash flow, and dividend since coming public 30 years ago.  It has grown into the world's eighth largest real estate investment trust (REIT), with nearly $58 billion in real estate.  The REIT believes it has a lot more growth ahead.
